== 评价 ==
《向日葵》在一些国际电影节上映。最后，它在2006年的圣塞瓦斯蒂安电影节上获得了最佳导演和评审团最佳摄影奖。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fortissimo.nl/catalogue/publicity.asp?filmID=205 |title=Sunflower, Publicity |publisher=Fortissimo Films |access-date=2007-10-29 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050122124724/http://www.fortissimo.nl/catalogue/publicity.asp?filmID=205 |archive-date=2005-01-22 |df= |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据13条评论为这部电影提供了69%的支持率，平均评分为6.1/10。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10005901-sunflower/|title=Sunflower (2007)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2021-01-22|archive-date=2012-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021224758/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10005901-sunflower/|dead-url=no}}</ref>根据[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]对四位评论家进行抽样并计算出64分（满分100分）的加权平均分，这部电影获得了“普遍好评”。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/sunflower|title=Sunflower|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2020-07-08|archive-date=2007-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070827101949/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/sunflower|dead-url=no}}</ref>

